title: 1000 Nudes - Uwe Scheid Collection (Photo Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / eng, ger, fra / 1994 taschen / 756 pages / ISBN10 3822855693 / 40.7 MB

This photographic collection offers a cross-section of the history of nude photography, ranging from early to experimental pictures. All the images are taken from the Uwe Scheid Collection, one of the largest and most important collections of erotic photography in the world
